#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
msgid "Console applications are mainly used to create utility, background processing and maintenance tasks."
msgstr "控制台应用程序主要用于创建实用工具、后台处理和维护任务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
msgid "If you're using [yiisoft/app](https://github.com/yiisoft/app) or [yiisoft/app-api](https://github.com/yiisoft/app-api), console support is already included.  You can access the entry point as:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "./yii\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "You can also provide your own storage using the [yiisoft/rbac](https://github.com/yiisoft/rbac) package."
msgid "If you want a standalone console-only application, use the [yiisoft/app-console](https://github.com/yiisoft/app-console) project template:"
msgstr "您还可以使用 [yiisoft/rbac](https://github.com/yiisoft/rbac) 包提供自己的存储。"

#. type: Fenced code block (sh)
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "composer create-project yiisoft/app-console your-project\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "You can learn more about the application template from the [yiisoft/app package documentation](https://github.com/yiisoft/app/blob/master/README.md)."
msgid "To add console support to an existing project from scratch, refer to the [yiisoft/yii-console package documentation](https://github.com/yiisoft/yii-console)."
msgstr "你可以从 [yiisoft/app 包文档](https://github.com/yiisoft/app/blob/master/README.md)中了解更多关于应用程序模板的信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
msgid "Out of the box only `serve` command is available. It's starting PHP built-in web server to serve the application locally."
msgstr "开箱即用只有 `serve` 命令可用。它启动 PHP 内置 Web 服务器在本地提供应用程序服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
msgid "Commands are executed with `symfony/console`. To create your own console command, you need to define a command:"
msgstr "命令使用 `symfony/console` 执行。要创建自己的控制台命令，您需要定义一个命令："

#. type: Fenced code block (php)
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<?php\n"
"namespace App\\Command\\Demo;\n"
"\n"
"use Symfony\\Component\\Console\\Attribute\\AsCommand;\n"
"use Symfony\\Component\\Console\\Command\\Command;\n"
"use Symfony\\Component\\Console\\Input\\InputArgument;\n"
"use Symfony\\Component\\Console\\Input\\InputInterface;\n"
"use Symfony\\Component\\Console\\Output\\OutputInterface;\n"
"use Symfony\\Component\\Console\\Style\\SymfonyStyle;\n"
"use Yiisoft\\Yii\\Console\\ExitCode;\n"
"\n"
"#[AsCommand(\n"
"    name: 'demo:hello',\n"
"    description: 'Echoes hello',\n"
"    \n"
")]\n"
"class HelloCommand extends Command\n"
"{   \n"
"    public function configure(): void\n"
"    {\n"
"        $this            \n"
"            ->setHelp('This command serves for demo purpose')\n"
"            ->addArgument('name', InputArgument::OPTIONAL, 'Name to greet', 'anonymous');\n"
"    }\n"
"\n"
"    protected function execute(InputInterface $input, OutputInterface $output): int\n"
"    {\n"
"        $io = new SymfonyStyle($input, $output);\n"
"\n"
"        $name = $input->getArgument('name');\n"
"        $io->success(\"Hello, $name!\");\n"
"        return ExitCode::OK;\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
msgid "Now register the command in `config/params.php`:"
msgstr "现在在 `config/params.php` 中注册该命令："

#. type: Fenced code block (php)
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"return [\n"
"    'yiisoft/yii-console' => [\n"
"        'commands' => [\n"
"            'demo:hello' => App\\Demo\\HelloCommand::class,\n"
"        ],\n"
"    ],    \n"
"];\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
msgid "After it's done, the command could be executed as"
msgstr "完成后，命令可以通过以下方式执行："

#. type: Fenced code block
#: ../src/guide/tutorial/console-applications.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "./yii demo:hello Alice\n"
msgstr ""

